┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                RunHaven Guide                                │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
┌ Actions ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│Launch is a four-step wizard: agent, workspace, review boundary, confirm      │
│launch.                                                                       │
│                                                                              │
│Home shows Cubby plus the selected agent, workspace, network, boundary, and   │
│next safe action.                                                             │
│                                                                              │
│Footers list only actions for the current screen. Use ? or F1 to return       │
│here.                                                                         │
│                                                                              │
│Secure-default plans launch with enter. Lower-security choices require        │
│typing run.                                                                   │
│                                                                              │
│Side flows: d dashboard/logs, h history/diffs, and g diagnostics/doctor.      │
│                                                                              │
│Display: p toggles Cubby. USAGE documents NO_COLOR, reduced motion, line      │
│mode, and light/dark palette environment controls.                            │
│                                                                              │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
     w workspace · r review · d dash · h history · g diag · p pet · esc home
               Every TUI action maps back to a named CLI command.
